    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240980/extras/90fd0ff5269133168a78687ca46b528d.avif?t=1762539019\" width=630 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This optional DLC is a great way to show your support and get something nice in return—all the art of <i>Sigh of the Abyss</i> collected in a single .pdf! Includes character art, illustrations and background art, plus a map of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes two files, one annotated and one without comments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240980/extras/0b1a4e2bc5b8e279240b8c9c3440361c.webp?t=1762539019\" width=630 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's recommended to enjoy the artbook <strong>after</strong> completing the game at least once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240980/extras/7aabb76d659a60082c46b0a0d6379f83.webp?t=1762539019\" width=630 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the Steam library, right-click the game and select Manage &gt; Browse local files.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PDF reader is required to open the artbook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WARNING</strong>: due to the  large size of the file, the initial loading time might take a while.</p>",
